    "text": "It's called hamburger pie."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 2.255,
    "endTime": 4.87,
    "text": "Hamburger pie."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 4.87,
    "endTime": 5.72,
    "text": "Yeah."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 5.72,
    "endTime": 9.76,
    "text": "So this is kind of a dessert in those days."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 9.76,
    "endTime": 13.74,
    "text": "Well, to be honest we didn't have much dessert in those days."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 13.74,
    "endTime": 17.183,
    "text": "This was a main course and dessert."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 17.183,
    "endTime": 19.766,
    "text": "(upbeat music)"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 25.394,
    "endTime": 26.226,
    "text": "Hi."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 26.227,
    "endTime": 27.06,
    "text": "Hi."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 27.06,
    "endTime": 27.892,
    "text": "Who are you two?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 27.893,
    "endTime": 31.454,
    "text": "I am Clara and this is my grandfather Ernie."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 31.454,
    "endTime": 35.0,
    "text": "I'm GG's grandmother, she calls me Mimi."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 35.0,
    "endTime": 38.16,
    "text": "This is my grandfather Preston."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 38.16,
    "endTime": 40.256,
    "text": "Grandfather, thank you."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 40.256,
    "endTime": 41.866,
    "text": "GG, what are you doing here with your grandma?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 41.866,
    "endTime": 43.949,
    "text": "Hm, let's take a guess."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 44.92,
    "endTime": 46.564,
    "text": "We're gonna do homework."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 46.564,
    "endTime": 48.02,
    "text": "No!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 48.02,
    "endTime": 57.190000000000005,
    "text": "I'm here because Clara wanted me to bring something that my mother, Kay, had made for me when I was a little guy that I liked and I remember."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 57.19,
    "endTime": 60.0,
    "text": "What foods did you like to eat when you were my age?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 60.0,
    "endTime": 64.64,
    "text": "When I was your age I ate whatever my mama gave me."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 64.64,
    "endTime": 65.626,
    "text": "You wouldn't believe it."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 65.626,
    "endTime": 68.31,
    "text": "We ate squirrels."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 68.31,
    "endTime": 69.143,
    "text": "What?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 69.143,
    "endTime": 76.56,
    "text": "Squirrels, my dad would shoot a squirrel, bring it home, fry it up, and we would have squirrel."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 76.56,
    "endTime": 77.393,
    "text": "What?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 77.393,
    "endTime": 78.27,
    "text": "Did you bring squirrel?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 79.41,
    "endTime": 80.243,
    "text": "No."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 80.243,
    "endTime": 81.076,
    "text": "What did you bring?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 81.076,
    "endTime": 82.33,
    "text": "Well it has meat in it."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 82.33,
    "endTime": 83.163,
    "text": "Should we bring it out?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 83.163,
    "endTime": 83.996,
    "text": "Yes."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 87.24,
    "endTime": 89.55,
    "text": "Clara, open your eyes."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 91.386,
    "endTime": 93.229,
    "text": "What's that?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 93.23,
    "endTime": 97.55000000000001,
    "text": "That is a good old fashioned Bisquick biscuit."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 97.55,
    "endTime": 98.88,
    "text": "Wow."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 98.88,
    "endTime": 101.393,
    "text": "It's probably stuck."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 102.99,
    "endTime": 103.83,
    "text": "What is it?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 103.83,
    "endTime": 104.95,
    "text": "I don't know."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 106.673,
    "endTime": 109.07000000000001,
    "text": "Bread, biscuits and gravy!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 109.07,
    "endTime": 110.669,
    "text": "How about a dumpling?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 110.67,
    "endTime": 112.483,
    "text": "Open your eyes, Cavalli."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 112.483,
    "endTime": 114.02300000000001,
    "text": "What do you call it?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 114.023,
    "endTime": 115.7,
    "text": "This is a bruncholoney sandwich."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 115.7,
    "endTime": 117.272,
    "text": "Bunch?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 117.272,
    "endTime": 118.26100000000001,
    "text": "Bruch."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 118.261,
    "endTime": 119.094,
    "text": "Bruncholoney."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 119.094,
    "endTime": 127.78,
    "text": "Yeah, because you know, we'd have breakfast, which would usually be cereal, and then before we went out to play we'd take a little sandwich so we wouldn't have to come back for lunch."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 127.78,
    "endTime": 130.113,
    "text": "So let's get to making this!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 133.566,
    "endTime": 136.88,
    "text": "Do I get the tiny bowl or the big bowl?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 136.88,
    "endTime": 137.98,
    "text": "Which?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 137.98,
    "endTime": 139.61999999999998,
    "text": "I want the big bowl!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 139.621,
    "endTime": 141.25,
    "text": "Of course you want the big bowl."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 141.25,
    "endTime": 143.147,
    "text": "Come back here, chicken."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 143.147,
    "endTime": 144.32899999999998,
    "text": "What is this stuff?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 144.33,
    "endTime": 158.119,
    "text": "It's chicken and dumplings and when I was little, I used to read cookbooks and I read this recipe and I wanted to make it and my mom said, \"Only if your dad's not home because he doesn't like his food mixed up.\""
  },
  {
    "startTime": 158.12,
    "endTime": 162.93,
    "text": "So we made it one time when my dad was gone and I loved it."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 162.93,
    "endTime": 164.91500000000002,
    "text": "Can I have more chicken please?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 164.915,
    "endTime": 167.666,
    "text": "Now this is what I made for myself."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 167.666,
    "endTime": 170.097,
    "text": "My mama didn't make this for me."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 170.097,
    "endTime": 175.07000000000002,
    "text": "Then we just put it on there and you take it and you smash it down."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 175.07,
    "endTime": 176.173,
    "text": "Put the top on there."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 180.0,
    "endTime": 181.12,
    "text": "Then you mash it down."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 184.82,
    "endTime": 186.78,
    "text": "When would you eat this?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 186.78,
    "endTime": 194.497,
    "text": "Well actually this would be kind of a good meal, this would be like maybe a Sunday, fancy meal, like fancy Sunday dinner."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 194.497,
    "endTime": 197.63000000000002,
    "text": "Did you have to dress up for Sunday dinner?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 197.63,
    "endTime": 201.167,
    "text": "That's funny, we had to dress for Sunday dinner."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 201.167,
    "endTime": 203.44,
    "text": "We didn't dress up."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 203.44,
    "endTime": 206.01,
    "text": "Let's do this together, 3, 2, 1."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 208.204,
    "endTime": 210.94,
    "text": "It's stuck in my teeth."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 210.94,
    "endTime": 213.067,
    "text": "But is it good?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 213.068,
    "endTime": 217.43,
    "text": "Yeah, do you think you were like me when you were a little kid?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 217.43,
    "endTime": 222.948,
    "text": "I was probably a little more active than you because once we had breakfast, we got kicked out of the house."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 222.948,
    "endTime": 224.35,
    "text": "Dang!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 224.35,
    "endTime": 225.896,
    "text": "We'd go out, we'd play baseball."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 225.896,
    "endTime": 230.303,
    "text": "We'd swim, we'd have rock fights."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 231.77,
    "endTime": 232.937,
    "text": "Somebody got hit like that."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 232.937,
    "endTime": 234.524,
    "text": "I got hit but I'd see them come, I'd duck."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 234.524,
    "endTime": 237.488,
    "text": "I never got hit in the face, but yeah."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 237.488,
    "endTime": 241.327,
    "text": "We'd have bb gun fights, one kid got his eye shot out."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 243.045,
    "endTime": 243.878,
    "text": "Really?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 243.878,
    "endTime": 245.95,
    "text": "Yeah, he didn't play with us no more."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 245.95,
    "endTime": 249.45999999999998,
    "text": "What I recognize in you is that you're busy."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 249.461,
    "endTime": 251.85000000000002,
    "text": "You're always doing something."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 251.85,
    "endTime": 255.32,
    "text": "You're always moving, you're always active."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 255.32,
    "endTime": 258.296,
    "text": "Yeah, you're like me in that way a lot and you know what it is?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 258.296,
    "endTime": 259.469,
    "text": "What?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 259.47,
    "endTime": 261.33000000000004,
    "text": "It's because you're a pretty bright little one."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 261.329,
    "endTime": 262.835,
    "text": "You wanna learn how to make this?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 262.836,
    "endTime": 263.66900000000004,
    "text": "Yeah."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 263.669,
    "endTime": 268.719,
    "text": "Yeah, we'll do that maybe next Wednesday on your early release day, that sounds like a good project."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 268.719,
    "endTime": 271.84,
    "text": "I found the last piece of chicken!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 271.84,
    "endTime": 274.07,
    "text": "Thank you for bringing this delicious dish."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 274.07,
    "endTime": 275.522,
    "text": "I will be eating the chicken."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 277.3,
    "endTime": 279.444,
    "text": "Thanks pop pop for coming here."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 279.444,
    "endTime": 280.40000000000003,
    "text": "Well thanks for inviting me."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 280.4,
    "endTime": 282.919,
    "text": "Thank you for sharing this food with me."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 282.92,
    "endTime": 284.492,
    "text": "You're welcome, wanna toast?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 284.492,
    "endTime": 285.923,
    "text": "Happy holidays."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 289.95,
    "endTime": 291.283,
    "text": "Bye!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 291.283,
    "endTime": 292.663,
    "text": "Peace."
  }
